data.description: Gorgeous 4 bedroom home with one full bedroom and a full bath downstairs with private entrance through garage. Open concept kitchen with white cabinetry, quartz counters, quartz waterfall through out the kitchen. Modern appliances. Vinyl plank flooring through the whole house. Plantation shutters downstairs, blinds upstairs. Updated doors through out the house closets, bedrooms and restrooms. Home was remodeled in 2020 with upgraded bathrooms and upgraded lighting through out. Glass sliding door leads to a recently built covered patio with ceiling fan and lighting. AC less than 5 years old. Located in a cul-de-sac in walking distance to Harvest Park in quiet Otay Ranch with the top rated schools, beautiful parks, public transportation, local shopping and easy freeway access. Low HOA fees.
